    "description": "<p>Padlet Pte. Ltd. builds and maintains Padlet (https://padlet.com), a tool that allows anyone to collaboratively create content on any platform, mobile or the web. We want to be the easiest way for anyone to do so.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The app is used by millions daily across the world. Our primary audience is students and educators from schools and tertiary institutions.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our team is comprised of forty five beautiful people who work out of Singapore, Australia, and the USA (where we are headquartered).&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Read about who we are at https://padlet.com/about/us.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Those of us based in Singapore will be focused primarily on building and maintaining features for the software.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Write us at hello@padlet.com if you have any questions. We'd love to hear from you.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
